our work

For four months I was interning at the South Caucasus Regional Office of the Heinrich Böll Foundation in Tbilisi. Since my time at the Foundation began early in the year, my first and main task consisted of summarizing and evaluating all projects from the passed year in order to draft an annual report for the BMZ in Germany. Writing this report right in the beginning of my internship gave me a good overview of the great variety of projects implemented by the HBF SC.
